{"id": 2641, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心 x ColorOS】为了打破生活既定边界带来的束缚感/焦虑感，你做过哪些努力？", "description": "承认吧，还是有许多人被生活框死在了原地，我们希望能帮到他们。（题图来自：pixabay）", "record_count": 10335, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181123110346Gjx9gruCewmhfnpO.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-11-23T03:07:08Z", "options": [{"id": 312832, "content": "给自己找做不完的事，完成一件事做下一件，直到疲惫", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1512520}, {"id": 313088, "content": "我要努力学习，抓紧一切时间，把业余爱好全部搁起来。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1264810}, {"id": 313089, "content": "深呼吸，看书？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1509246}, {"id": 330754, "content": "多询问自己内心，你真的想要什么，你真的需要什么，你真的在意什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1600624}, {"id": 312834, "content": "认识新事物，精进专业，健身，旅行", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 99741}, {"id": 313090, "content": "自我催眠说自己脸皮很厚", "image": "img/option/option/20181125222623B65pl8aSt7dEWAOn", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1511894}, {"id": 312838, "content": "过的随心一点，任性一点", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1512535}, {"id": 313094, "content": "学会思考，总结方法论。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1514542}, {"id": 312839, "content": "996", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1500742}, {"id": 312840, "content": "放下设定的偶像包袱～😏", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 724535}, {"id": 313096, "content": "身体和灵魂，总要有一个在路上的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1514595}, {"id": 312841, "content": "和家人吵架，变的患得患失，每天都在拷问自己，差一点就抑郁了", "image": "img/option/option/20181124000823Kr1lXy0mQLT7Fgnt", "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1512550}, {"id": 312842, "content": "重新架构价值观，学会区分自己和他人在所谓的重要上的认识。然后会发现一切皆空，人生只要将自己喜欢的事情做好就够了", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 773145}, {"id": 314890, "content": "离开原地，去尝试需要跳一跳才能够到的地方。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1524108}, {"id": 312843, "content": "去夜店假装成另一个人  然后第二天回归自己的生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1478077}, {"id": 313099, "content": "创业是我最大的努力。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1510380}, {"id": 312845, "content": "不是说color抄袭Flyme么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1275828}, {"id": 313103, "content": "但行好事，莫问前程。\n抱怨再多都没用，倒不如埋头苦干。\n土星回归，会有大礼包的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 966667}, {"id": 313104, "content": "周末坐公交去找书店，待一天", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1514670}, {"id": 313106, "content": "想方设法更加自己对于本身的弱小感触度，让自己使劲相信强者应该克服并战胜这种情绪", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1514754}, {"id": 314131, "content": "更多的独处时间，更多的阅读和音乐，适当饮酒，充足的睡眠。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1271976}, {"id": 312853, "content": "复读，跨专业，尝试，失败", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1511493}, {"id": 313109, "content": "画画 读书 学习新语言 做手工……总之不能让自己闲下来", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1514826}, {"id": 314134, "content": "周末去到汉堡王，吃一个四层汉堡！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1520392}, {"id": 312855, "content": "建立习惯 可真的很难\n但建立花钱的习惯很容易\n有规律的去听音乐会吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1512572}, {"id": 312857, "content": "独处\n计划\n执行", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 297429}, {"id": 312858, "content": "扮演不同的角色。你可以是反差很大的斜杠青年，你可以是个志愿者，你可以是个背包客。可以有边界，但一定不能被束缚，要做也要做个多边形，而不是死板的四方。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1512587}, {"id": 312859, "content": "面对，看明白了也就放松不焦虑了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1511750}, {"id": 312860, "content": "洗澡，换上干净的衣服，背上书包去图书馆。\n感觉这个过程很有仪式感", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1512599}, {"id": 313116, "content": "有机会认识比你层次更高的人 然后多和他们聊聊，你就会觉得我这点焦虑算什么 难道不应该多想怎么努力么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1514870}, {"id": 312861, "content": "洗澡 看书 睡觉 第二天继续努力", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1512618}, {"id": 314143, "content": "看各种不同的大学教材：自然地理学、系统解剖学、大众传播去、基础生态学、社会心理学、微观经济学、分子细胞学、结构力学、西方美术等等", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1520406}, {"id": 312864, "content": "选择，以及放弃！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 662194}, {"id": 312865, "content": "一个人环游世界，做任何自己想做的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1510601}, {"id": 312866, "content": "睡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1509139}, {"id": 312611, "content": "不给自己立太多人设、少立flag", "image": null, "praise_count": 816, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 312612, "content": "尝试发现社交恐惧的克服原来只需要简单的迈出家门", "image": null, "praise_count": 550, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 312868, "content": "讨厌办公室复杂人际关系，想自己独处。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1512652}, {"id": 312613, "content": "讲真的，我觉得旅行不能解决一切，但却可以让你心里装的下更多", "image": null, "praise_count": 2258, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 312614, "content": "在生活里积极地去运用断舍离法则", "image": null, "praise_count": 805, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 312615, "content": "多交朋友，你会看到不同的生活方式（顺带发现自己活的多紧绷）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1397, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 312616, "content": "不再积极给自己设任务定目标之后，发量明显增加", "image": null, "praise_count": 115, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 312623, "content": "离家出走！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1235379}, {"id": 312624, "content": "从不评价任何人的选择和方向，保证自己每天都有真实的爽朗笑声！", "image": null, "praise_count": 94, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1472525}, {"id": 312625, "content": "在健身房里释放汗水，忘记烦恼", "image": null, "praise_count": 136, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1482927}, {"id": 312626, "content": "放空吧，无所事事看一部电影听一首歌，让情绪放空", "image": null, "praise_count": 116, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1442385}, {"id": 312629, "content": "辞职远走", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1437481}, {"id": 312630, "content": "一昧的循规蹈矩将会带来迟滞的发展", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1344200}, {"id": 313142, "content": "看书，学习。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 290842}, {"id": 312631, "content": "拼命考试\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1151252}]}